<p style="font-family:Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#000000; margin:0 0 10px 0; padding:0;">Dear Colleague</p>
<p style="font-family:Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#000000; margin:0 0 10px 0; padding:0;">Your account: <strong>{$account->name}</strong></p>
<p style="font-family:Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#000000; margin:0 0 10px 0; padding:0;">You might aware that our system sent you a termination email regarding the old Study Skills Success earlier today. It just means that your old Study Skills Success is no longer available, and that you can start to use your new, upgraded Study Skills Success V9 from  today onwards.</p>
<p style="font-family:Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#000000; margin:0 0 10px 0; padding:0;">The new version is a great improvement. Here are just five of the new features:<br />
1. Two new units on Critical Thinking and Independent Learning<br />
2. Video introductions for each unit, featuring teachers and students.<br />
3. A new section on Presentations in the Speaking unit.<br />
4. A more structured learning path with learning objectives for each exercise and a review section for each unit.<br />
5. More activities and more use of authentic materials, including a BBC lecture.</p>
<p style="font-family:Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#000000; margin:0 0 10px 0; padding:0;">For more information, please visit: <a href="http://www.clarityenglish.com/program/studyskills.php" target="_blank">www.clarityenglish.com/program/studyskills.php</a></p>
<p style="font-family:Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#000000; margin:0 0 10px 0; padding:0;">The upgrade is free of charge, part of the service we provide with your subscription.</p>
<p style="font-family:Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#000000; margin:0 0 10px 0; padding:0;">Apologies for the confusion that the earlier email may have caused. It was not as clear as it should have been. Please feel free to contact us if you have any questions. Any comments will be appreciated.</p>
